Class DolphinWindow<M>

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.stage.Window
      • com.canoo.dolphin.client.javafx.stage.DolphinWindow<M>
  • Type Parameters:
    M - type of the model
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventTarget

    public class DolphinWindow<M>
extends Window
    A JavaFX Window that contains the view of a AbstractViewBinder and will automatically call AbstractViewBinder.destroy() when the stage becomes hidden.
